          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Shalom Hills International School is the best school, I have come across. Co-curricular activities are well built in with academics. They organizes various events and activities like academic presentation, annual assemblies, sports events, inter school competition, festivals and celebrations etc.This School is a perfect place for overall development of a child.\nThe school has decent infrastructure, although ACs have been installed last year as per the parent’s request. A special thanks to school management for being so considerate.\nThe teachers at SHIS are hard-working and nurture each and every student for their bright future. Shalom strives to make each child feel appreciated and nurtured both mentally and emotionally. The Management, Principal, Vice Principal, teachers and the entire admin staff is very cordial and extremely caring towards children.\nOverall Shalom is value for money.\nThis is one institution which is committed to fostering a nurturing and stimulating environment that cultivates academic excellence, character development, and personal growth.\n\nI highly recommend SHALOM.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
